## Name of the node
-name bondy@127.0.0.1

## Cookie for distributed erlang
-setcookie bondy

## Explicit connections only.
-connect_all false

## Hidden nodes
-hidden

## Max processes
+P 2000000

## Kernel polling
+K true

## Async I/O threads
+A 64

## Increase distribution port buffer size.
+zdbbl 32768

## Enable multi_time_warp
+C multi_time_warp
